-- Britain Raises Its Terrorism Alert to `Substantial' Due to IRA Dissidents
-- B y   C o l m   H e a t l e y
-- 2010-09-24T15:50:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-24/britain-raises-terror-threat-level-to-substantial-due-to-ira-dissidents.html
The threat level from Irish
terrorists to the U.K. has been raised from “moderate” to
“substantial,” the  British Broadcasting Corp . reported, citing
comments from Britain’s Home Secretary,  Theresa May .  May said an attack is a “strong possibility” and the
information is being released to encourage people to remain
vigilant, according to the report. May made the statement after
receiving information from the director-general of Britain’s
security service, she was cited as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Colm Heatley  in Belfast at 
